flowchart TD
    A["ResourceManager receives Application resource requests"] --> B["Scheduler scans queue hierarchy from root"]
    B --> C{"Which queue has lowest used / configured capacity ratio?"}
    C -->|Queue X| D{"Is Queue X running and under its maxCapacity?"}
    D -- No --> E["Skip Queue X and select next best queue"]
    D -- Yes --> F["Assess active applications in Queue X"]
    F --> G{"Is queue ordering-policy fair or fifo?"}
    G -- fifo --> H["Sort applications by submission time"]
    G -- fair --> I["Sort applications by fair resource share allocation ratios"]
    H --> J["Select top application"]
    I --> J
    J --> K{"Is user resource limit exceeded for top application owner?"}
    K -- Yes --> L["Skip application, assess next in queue"]
    K -- No --> M["Assign container lease and generate security container token"]
